Functions:

Matrix Style Effect

The letters fall down in a "matrix" style while the text is output.
Real-time color changes and random positions for maximum dynamics.
Moving error messages

The fake error windows appear in random positions and move automatically.
Full screen and text scroller

Hacker text is output in a central window, while matrix animations run outside.
Progress bar remains

The system takeover is represented by a realistic loading bar.
Easily terminable

Press Escape to exit the full screen, or Ctrl+C to end the simulation.
